Package com.group11.classicmodels

Class CRUD

java.lang.Object
com.group11.classicmodels.CRUD
public class CRUD extends Object
CRUD operations for database interaction. Handles Create, Read, Update, Delete, and Search operations on a database.
Author:
Christian Douglas Farnes Fancy
